'''戈马'''（{{lang-fr|Goma}}）位于[[剛果民主共和國|剛果民主共和國]]东部，为[[北基伍省|北基伍省]]<!--(旧省:[[北基伍省|北基伍省]])-->首府，2021年人口總數為670,000。<ref name="population">{{cite web|url=https://www.macrotrends.net/cities/205453/goma/population#:~:text=The%20metro%20area%20population%20of,a%206.19%25%20increase%20from%202017.|title=剛果共和國地區人口普查報告2021|date=2021|access-date=January 10, 2021|archive-date=2020-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926183325/https://www.macrotrends.net/cities/205453/goma/population#:~:text=The%20metro%20area%20population%20of,a%206.19%25%20increase%20from%202017.}}</ref>地处[[基伍湖|基伍湖]]北岸，[[尼拉贡戈火山|尼拉贡戈火山]]南麓，与[[卢旺达|卢旺达]]城市[[吉塞尼|吉塞尼]]相邻。

